**Summary:** This documentation covers the Google Analytics 4 (iOS/Android) streaming integration for Amplitude Activation, which forwards events and users from Amplitude to GA4 mobile apps using Firebase App ID and Measurement Protocol API Secret, requiring App Instance ID mapping and supporting both event and user property forwarding.

